    <item>
      <title>危机缓解，英国商店通胀率降至接近零</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/inflation-in-uk-shops-falls-close-to-zero-lowest-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国商店的通货膨胀率自 2021 年 10 月以来首次降至接近零，这一新迹象表明家庭预算压力正在缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/inflation-in-uk-shops-falls-close-to-zero-lowest-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉加德称欧洲央行需要时间来权衡通胀不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德和她的首席经济学家表示，欧洲央行目前还没有足够的证据表明通胀威胁已经过去——这加剧了人们对央行本月将暂停降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/lagarde-says-ecb-will-need-time-to-weigh-inflation-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
